      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "Paper does not describe a modular 'manual callpeak pipeline' with separate steps. MACS is presented as an integrated algorithm with a single command-line interface, not as decomposable subcommands. The concepts (pileup, local-lambda, scoring, peak calling) exist within MACS but are not presented as separate pipeline stages.",
