      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Estimate local background noise in ChIP-Seq data by computing bias tracks at multiple genomic scales (fragment length d, 1 kb slocal, and 10 kb llocal windows) from control samples, then combining them to generate a normalized local lambda track.",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
